<subSubSection pageId="179" pageNumber="180" type="discussion">
<paragraph blockId="179.[151,1437,798,1473]" pageId="179" pageNumber="180">
REMARKS: 
<bibRefCitation author="Rondani, C." box="[268,519,1195,1221]" pageId="179" pageNumber="180" pagination="187 - 198" refId="ref371214" refString="Rondani, C. (1876 d) Species italicae ordinis dipterorum (Muscaria Rndn.) collectae et observatae. Stirps XXIV. Chylizinae Rndn. Bullettino delle Societa Entomologica Italiana, 8 (3), 187 - 198." type="journal article" year="1876">Rondani (1876d: 190)</bibRefCitation>
described both sexes of 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Rondani" authorityYear="1876" box="[804,974,1195,1221]" class="Insecta" family="Psilidae" genus="Psila" kingdom="Animalia" order="Diptera" pageId="179" pageNumber="180" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="bertolinii">
<emphasis box="[804,974,1195,1221]" italics="true" pageId="179" pageNumber="180">Psila bertolinii</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
without specifying either the 
<taxonomicName box="[1319,1405,1195,1221]" family="Number" pageId="179" pageNumber="26" rank="family">number</taxonomicName>
or the length of the specimens: “ 
<emphasis box="[538,1034,1231,1257]" italics="true" pageId="179" pageNumber="180">
<taxonomicName box="[538,587,1231,1256]" genus="Mas" pageId="179" pageNumber="180" rank="species" species="raro">raro</taxonomicName>
lectus uterque sexus a Cl. De Bertolini
</emphasis>
[both sexes rarely collected by Mr. De Bertolini]”. 
<bibRefCitation author="Soos, A." box="[372,577,1266,1293]" pageId="179" pageNumber="180" pagination="155 - 158" refId="ref373844" refString="Soos, A. (1982 b) Untersuchungen des Typenmaterials der Rondani'schen Sammlung. 1. Psilidae (Diptera). Folia Entomologica Hungarica, 43 (1), 155 - 158." type="journal article" year="1982">Soós (1982b: 156)</bibRefCitation>
designated a 
<typeStatus box="[727,830,1267,1293]" pageId="179" pageNumber="180">lectotype</typeStatus>
(
<specimenCount box="[844,866,1267,1293]" pageId="179" pageNumber="180" type="male">♂</specimenCount>
) and 
<typeStatus box="[928,1079,1267,1293]" pageId="179" pageNumber="180">paralectotype</typeStatus>
(
<specimenCount box="[1096,1115,1267,1293]" pageId="179" pageNumber="180" type="female">♀</specimenCount>
). Rondani spelled this nominal species as “ 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Rondani" authorityYear="1876" box="[373,477,1303,1329]" class="Insecta" family="Psilidae" genus="Psila" kingdom="Animalia" order="Diptera" pageId="179" pageNumber="180" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="bertolinii">
<emphasis box="[373,477,1303,1329]" italics="true" pageId="179" pageNumber="180">bertolinii</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
” in his key (p. 189) and as “ 
<emphasis box="[805,901,1303,1329]" italics="true" pageId="179" pageNumber="180">bertolini</emphasis>
” in his description (p. 190) and index (p. 198). 
<bibRefCitation author="Becker, T." box="[199,419,1338,1365]" pageId="179" pageNumber="180" pagination="1 - 273" refId="ref345239" refString="Becker, T. (1905) Cyclorrapha Schizophora: Holometopa. In: Becker T., Bezzi M., Kertesz K. &amp; Steins, P. (Eds.), Katalog der palaarktischen Dipteren. Band IV. G. Wesselenyi in Hodmezovasarhely, Budapest, pp. 1 - 273." type="book chapter" year="1905">Becker (1905: 159)</bibRefCitation>
<bibRefCitation author="Hennig, W." box="[427,636,1339,1366]" pageId="179" pageNumber="180" pagination="1 - 38" refId="ref352890" refString="Hennig, W. (1941) 41. Psilidae. In: Lindner, E. (Ed.), Die Fliegen der Palaearktischen Region. Band 5. Lieferung 140. E. Schweizerbart, Stuttgart, pp. 1 - 38." type="book chapter" year="1941">Hennig (1941: 16)</bibRefCitation>
and 
<bibRefCitation author="Soos, A." box="[692,901,1338,1365]" pageId="179" pageNumber="180" pagination="155 - 158" refId="ref373844" refString="Soos, A. (1982 b) Untersuchungen des Typenmaterials der Rondani'schen Sammlung. 1. Psilidae (Diptera). Folia Entomologica Hungarica, 43 (1), 155 - 158." type="journal article" year="1982">Soós (1982b: 156)</bibRefCitation>
listed this nominal species as “ 
<emphasis box="[1258,1354,1339,1365]" italics="true" pageId="179" pageNumber="180">bertolini</emphasis>
”, 
<bibRefCitation author="Soos, A." pageId="179" pageNumber="180" refId="ref373917" refString="Soos, A. (1984 a) Family Psilidae. In: Soos, A. &amp; Papp, L. (Eds.), Catalogue of Palaearctic Diptera. Volume 9. Micropezidae - Agromyzidae. Elsevier Science Publishers, Amsterdam &amp; Akademiai Kiado, Budapest, pp. 28 - 35." type="book" year="1984">Soós (1984a: 29)</bibRefCitation>
and 
<bibRefCitation author="Nartshuk, E. P. &amp; Papp, L. &amp; Raspi, A. &amp; Rivosecchi, L." box="[386,665,1374,1401]" pageId="179" pageNumber="180" pagination="1 - 8" refId="ref360754" refString="Nartshuk, E. P., Papp, L., Raspi, A. &amp; Rivosecchi, L. (1995) Diptera Nerioidea, Diopsoidea, Lauxanioidea. In: Minelli, A., Ruffo, S. &amp; La Posta, S. (Eds.), Checklist delle specie della fauna italiana. 73. Calderini, Bologna, pp. 1 - 8." type="book chapter" year="1995">
Nartshuk 
<emphasis box="[496,554,1375,1401]" italics="true" pageId="179" pageNumber="180">et al.</emphasis>
(1995: 4)
</bibRefCitation>
listed it as “ 
<emphasis box="[809,928,1375,1401]" italics="true" pageId="179" pageNumber="180">
<taxonomicName authorityName="Rondani" authorityYear="1876" box="[809,919,1375,1401]" class="Insecta" family="Psilidae" genus="Psila" kingdom="Animalia" order="Diptera" pageId="179" pageNumber="180" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="bertolinii">bertolinii</taxonomicName>
”
</emphasis>
. 
<bibRefCitation author="O'Hara, J. E. &amp; Cerretti, P. &amp; Pape, T. &amp; Evenhuis, N. L." box="[943,1231,1375,1401]" pageId="179" pageNumber="180" pagination="1 - 268" refId="ref361577" refString="O'Hara, J. E., Cerretti, P., Pape, T. &amp; Evenhuis, N. L. (2011) Nomenclatural studies toward a world list of Diptera genus-group names. Part II: Camillo Rondani. Zootaxa, 3141, 1 - 268. https: // doi. org / 10.11646 / zootaxa. 3141.1.1" type="journal article" year="2011">
O’Hara 
<emphasis box="[1035,1085,1375,1401]" italics="true" pageId="179" pageNumber="180">et al</emphasis>
. (2011: 207)
</bibRefCitation>
listed both names and, acting as First Revisers (according to I.C.Z.N. 1999: Article 24.2.3), they determined “ 
<emphasis box="[1242,1362,1411,1437]" italics="true" pageId="179" pageNumber="180">
<taxonomicName authorityName="Rondani" authorityYear="1876" box="[1242,1352,1411,1437]" class="Insecta" family="Psilidae" genus="Psila" kingdom="Animalia" order="Diptera" pageId="179" pageNumber="180" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="bertolinii">bertolinii</taxonomicName>
”
</emphasis>
as the correct original spelling and “ 
<emphasis box="[533,645,1447,1473]" italics="true" pageId="179" pageNumber="180">bertolini”</emphasis>
as the incorrect original spelling
</paragraph>
